{"tid":1378730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭聽日3點被辭職！！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T19:29:30.000Z","uid":146883,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e2be8bf88c7290098abe5f505dc739f7984d1e6c","tid":1378730,"uid":146883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"今晚開始不斷有人放風林鄭聽日3點被辭職！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家記住</span></span>，五大訴求入面係冇林鄭下台既。落台還落台，抗爭還抗爭，係兩回事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港的深層次問題，主要係制度問題</span></span>，更核心既其實係主權問題，而唔單單係領導人的問題。所以無論聽日三點林鄭患淋病又好，生花柳又好，落台又好，繼續「迎難而上」又好，大家緊記要毋忘初衷、堅守原則，堅持到底，就會勝利！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係要雙普選！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e9aaaec385a4cafb61c6b73a5a8fe1f1667a3b4","tid":1378730,"uid":51801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"冇錯，推"},{"pid":"d3b907159ab0b732b6e2c7c0183f8574a1ba0d00","tid":1378730,"uid":257736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"佢落台都唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcd2592c8abf178762946d9420c5c9921a22508","tid":1378730,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c77b4ef8b0e522ade5faa1a14044c5e3c4f104d","tid":1378730,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdba2d86908e5e39112f28601bb0616c9f3c1c16","tid":1378730,"uid":146883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf3e69770f785e1da74329760e9f0bae9997aa5","tid":1378730,"uid":85803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re